track_notes: You leave A-12 highway at Arma di Taggia exit. You follow SP548 up to Molini di Triora, just before the town you turn left SP65 following Colle della Melosa sign.
track_title: I/LG-303 Monte Pietravecchia dal Colle della Melosa

track_notes:
The first Summit :  Pietra Vecchia easy and near 8 points.
The second Summit Toraggio far and harder-to-rise 6 points .  So you can choice what you want do.

Long path to the second summit ( Toraggio ) via Passo Dragurina. The last part is steep between rocks, in southern exposition.
